# vPantry updated API
To run server locally for development, run `node src` from project root directory.

Postman collections have various example requests.

Postman collection for locally running vPantryAPI:
[![Run in Postman](https://run.pstmn.io/button.svg)](https://app.getpostman.com/run-collection/dd814c19981e4bcbd166#?env%5BvPantryAPI%)

[![Run in Postman](https://run.pstmn.io/button.svg)](https://app.getpostman.com/run-collection/e966bf200ccd13da8790#?env%5BvPantryAPI%)
